{"questionId":"3903","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Lutetium-177 is used in radiotherapy. It emits beta radiation when it decays.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>The half-life of lutetium-177 is 6.73 days. Determine the percentage of a sample of lutetium-177 remaining after 14.0 days.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>number of half-lives = <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{t}{{{t_{^{\\frac{1}{2}}}}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>t</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi></mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp;= 2.08</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{N\\left( t \\right)}}{{{N_0}}} = {0.5^{\\frac{{14.0}}{{6.73}}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>N</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>N</mi>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mn>0.5</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mfrac>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>14.0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>6.73</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\lambda&nbsp; = \">\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n</math></span> «<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{\\text{ln}}2}}{{{t_{^{\\frac{1}{2}}}}}} = \\frac{{{\\text{ln}}2}}{{6.73}} = \">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>ln</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi></mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mrow>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>ln</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>6.73</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n</math></span>»&nbsp;0.103 «day<sup>–1</sup>»</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{N\\left( t \\right)}}{{{N_0}}} = {e^{ - 0.103\\, \\times 14.0}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>N</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>N</mi>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>−</mo>\n        <mn>0.103</mn>\n        <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n        <mo>×</mo>\n        <mn>14.0</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>23.6 «%»</p>\n<p><em>Award<strong> [2]</strong> for correct final answer.</em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3903","referenceCode":"17N.3.hl.TZ0.21b","subjectId":"45-dp-chemistry-last-assessment-2024","title":"The half-life of lutetium-177 is 6.73 days. Determine the percentage of a sample of lutetium-177 remaining after 14.0 days.","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":